[30;1m9 | [0m[35mterminating properly. The Azure Service Bus SDK uses the Azure uAMQP library[0m
[30;1m10 | [0m[35mwhich in turn creates some threads. If the AzureServiceBus Channel is closed,[0m
[30;1m11 | [0m[35msaid threads will be closed properly, but it seems there are times when Celery[0m
